    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((v0 / (v0 + 0.22 * tmp + 0.11)) * ((v2 + 0.73 * v1 + 0.86) / (v0 + 0.28 * v1 + 0.32)))
    v1 = v1
    v0 = (wp.cos(0.76) - (wp.abs(v0 + 0.40) / v1))
    v0 = (tmp * v2)
    tmp = v2
    v1 = (0.64 - 0.11)
    tmp = (v1 / (wp.sin(v1 + 0.84) - wp.cos(v2 + 1.00)))
    data[tid] = v0
